#: .\chemical_spray.json
msgid "sprayable fungicide"
msgid_plural "sprayable fungicides"
msgstr[0] "可喷洒杀菌剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sprayable fungicide'}
#: .\chemical_spray.json
msgid ""
"Fungicide enhanced with sulfur to create sprayable anti-fungal ammo for the "
"chemical thrower.  Best be used with some kind of mask or mouth protection."
msgstr "添加硫磺增强的杀菌剂，制成用于化学喷射器的可喷洒抗真菌弹药。最好配合某种面罩或口部防护使用。"

#: .\chemical_spray.json
msgid "sprayable insecticide"
msgid_plural "sprayable insecticides"
msgstr[0] "可喷洒杀虫剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sprayable insecticide'}
#: .\chemical_spray.json
msgid ""
"Strong sprayable insecticide ammo for the chemical thrower.  Best be used "
"with some kind of mask or mouth protection."
msgstr "用于化学喷射器的强力可喷洒杀虫剂弹药。最好配合某种面罩或口部防护使用。"

#: .\fgrenades.json
msgid "makeshift fungicidal jug grenade"
msgid_plural "makeshift fungicidal jug grenades"
msgstr[0] "临时杀菌罐式手榴弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift fungicidal jug grenade'}
#: .\fgrenades.json
msgid ""
"This is a jug filled with homemade fungicidal solution.  Use this item to "
"open the container and then use like an active fungicidal grenade.  In five "
"turns it will begin to expel a volatile spray that is highly toxic to fungal"
" life forms and humans."
msgstr ""
"这是一个装满自制杀菌溶液的罐子。使用此物品打开容器，然后像激活的杀菌手榴弹一样使用。五回合后，它将开始释放挥发性喷雾，对真菌生命体和人类剧毒。"

#: .\fgrenades.json
msgid "makeshift fungicidal can grenade"
msgid_plural "makeshift fungicidal can grenades"
msgstr[0] "临时杀菌罐式手榴弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift fungicidal can grenade'}
#: .\fgrenades.json
msgid ""
"This is a used can filled with homemade fungicidal solution.  Use this item "
"to turn it into an active homemade fungicidal grenade.  In five turns it "
"will begin to expel a volatile spray that is highly toxic to fungal life "
"forms and humans."
msgstr "这是一个装满自制杀菌溶液的旧罐子。使用此物品将其变成激活的自制杀菌手榴弹。五回合后，它将开始释放挥发性喷雾，对真菌生命体和人类剧毒。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Homemade Fungicide"
msgstr "自制杀菌剂"

#. ~ Description for Homemade Fungicide
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Now you can make homemade fungicide and anti-fungus bombs using bleach and "
"ammonia! Also adds toxic gas effects to fungicidal and insecticidal gas. "
"Intended to help combat and balance cdda's fungal factor and get more people"
" playing with fungus."
msgstr ""
"现在你可以用漂白剂和氨水制作自制杀菌剂和抗真菌炸弹！同时为杀菌和杀虫气体添加毒性气体效果。旨在帮助对抗和平衡CDDA的真菌因素，并让更多人尝试与真菌互动。"
